<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavaruṣaṁbulu 1212 gunēṁṭṭi pratāpavī
<lb n="2" break="no"/>raśrīnarasiṁhyadēvaru pravarddhamāna vijayarājya 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>saṁvvatsaraṁbulu 15 gu śrāhi makara śuddha 10
<lb n="4"/>yu guruvāramuna cīkaṭiAdhi kārulaina gatiku
<lb n="5" break="no"/>varumaṁḍalīka prōlujīyyakoḍuku prōlujīyya
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṇa śrīkūrmmanāthuni sannidhini Ākhaṁḍḍadīpamu (<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>) Ācaṁdrā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>rkkamu celluṭakuṁ beṭṭina mōdālu 25 nu Ī dīpadaṁḍḍuna
<lb n="8" break="no"/>kuṁ beṭṭina gaṁḍḍamāḍa 1 nuṁgā dīpamu 1 <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> vīra druggādē
<lb n="9" break="no"/>vikiṁ beṭṭiṇa mōdavu 1 nū vīru siddhanāthadēvarakuṁ beṭṭina mō
<lb n="10" break="no"/>dālu 2 <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Īdharmmapu Ācaṁdrārkkamugāṁ jelluṭaku tirupa
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ti śrīvaiṣṇavarakṣa(ḥ) <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> jīyyana peṭṭina mallākālu Īddaṟu ca
<lb n="12" break="no"/>nnadiparissa<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>yya sēya<note n="447-1">The inscription is left unfinished.</note>
</p>

